# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Telegram Task Management Bot — Environment Variables
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Copy this file to a new file named exactly: .env
#    (cp .env.example .env  on Mac/Linux)
#
# 2. Fill in your values below.
#
# 3. Never commit your .env file to version control!
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Your Telegram bot token from @BotFather
# How to get it: Open Telegram → search @BotFather → /newbot → follow prompts
BOT_TOKEN=your_bot_token_here

# Your personal Telegram user ID (this makes you the admin)
# How to get it: Open Telegram → search @userinfobot → /start → copy your ID
ADMIN_ID=your_telegram_user_id_here
